data.description: This spacious house features a stunning, large, covered back deck, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy cozy evenings by the rock fireplace and admire the shiplap ceiling details. The master bath boasts a double vanity and luxurious large soaker tub. The kitchen offers beautiful cabinetry with solid surface countertops with a stylish backsplash along with built-in stainless steel appliances. Hardwood floors add elegance throughout, and a sizeable back yard completes this charming home. Call today and make this home yours!
